Problem Statement 10: Please compute the following: a) P(Z > 1.26), . P(Z < âˆ’0.86), P(Z > âˆ’1.37), P(âˆ’1.25 < Z < 0.37), . P(Z â‰¤ âˆ’4.6) b) Find the value ğ‘§ such that ğ‘ƒ(ğ‘ > ğ‘§) = 0.05 c) Find the value of ğ‘§ such that ğ‘ƒ(âˆ’ğ‘§ < ğ‘ < ğ‘§) = 0.99


print("P(Z > 1.26) : ",1-(st.norm.cdf(1.26)))
print("P(Z < âˆ’0.86):",st.norm.cdf(-0.86))
print("P(Z > âˆ’1.37):",1-(st.norm.cdf(-1.37)))
print("P(âˆ’1.25 < Z < 0.37):",(st.norm.cdf(0.37)-st.norm.cdf(-1.25)))
print("P(Z â‰¤ âˆ’4.6):",1-(st.norm.cdf(4.6)))
print("value ğ‘§ such that ğ‘ƒ(ğ‘ > ğ‘§) = 0.05:",np.absolute(st.norm.ppf(0.05)))
print("value of ğ‘§ such that ğ‘ƒ(âˆ’ğ‘§ < ğ‘ < ğ‘§):",st.norm.ppf(0.99))
